<p>x) You say: “Gasteropoda or marine univalve shells.” But the order includes not only marine forms, but also freshwater and land-animals, as you mention yourself a few lines later “pulmoniferous Gasteropoda or landshells.” So I think it might be better to leave out the “marine”.<ref target="#foot.f3"/></p>
<p>I should not like to worry you with requests, but if you could spare a clean copy of the Descent of Man I should be exceedingly obliged to you.<ref target="#foot.f4"/></p>
<p>Believe me | Yours very sincerely | J. Victor Carus</p> 
